An oddly formed pool of frozen water that seems to be formed of small frozen droplets of water.

This tunnel looks like it's been forcibly dug into the icy mountainside. It slopes downward at a sharp angle. It looks like it'll be a nightmare to try to climb back out.

All around the entrance there are signs which indicate the passage of beast and humanoid alike - and plenty of blood. The sounds coming from within indicate that the beast laired here is an incredibly powerful foe: far more so than any of the other beasts around here. Best to go in only when you have finished your training and found some friends to help.
